 teams in an Agile environment.\"},{\"skill\":\"VS Code\",\"category\":\"Related Skills\",\"experience_level\":\"Intermediate\",\"estimated_duration\":\"1–2 Years\",\"evidence_strength\":\"Moderate Evidence\",\"evidence_source\":\"Skills Section Only\",\"usage_context\":\"Listed as a common development tool in the technical skills section.\"}],\"additional_skills\":[\"Flutter\",\"Android Studio\",\"Firebase\",\"Figma\",\"Canva\",\"Wireframing\",\"Prototyping\",\"Python\",\"LLMs\",\"AI Chatbot Development\",\"Bubble.io\",\"XAMPP\",\"phpMyAdmin\",\"Eclipse IDE\",\"Apache NetBeans IDE\",\"IoT Sensors\",\"Embedded C\",\"GPS Module\",\"GSM Module\",\"Leadership\",\"Critical Thinking\",\"Time Management\"],\"certifications_found\":[\"Python for Beginners in University of Moratuwa\",\"Web Design for Beginners in University of Moratuwa\",\"Introduction to Android Studio Course in Simplilearn\",\"UI/UX for Beginners in Great Learning\",\"ReactJS for Beginners in Simplilearn\"],\"experience_summary\":\"BSc (Hons) Software Engineering undergraduate with 6 months of software developer internship experience, skilled in web and mobile application development. Proficient in JavaScript, React, Node.js, PHP, and MySQL. Experienced in RESTful API integration, UI/UX design, and software testing. Demonstrated strong problem-solving, analytical, and communication skills, with collaboration in Agile environments. Utilized Git and GitHub for version control.\",\"fully_demonstrated_skills\":[\"JavaScript\",\"React\",\"HTML\",\"CSS\",\"Java\",\"Git\",\"Problem-solving\",\"Communication Skills\",\"Node.js\",\"Next.js\"],\"partially_demonstrated_skills\":[\"Work with SQL Server and Oracle databases to write optimized queries and manage database structures\",\"Write clean, scalable, and maintainable code following software development best practices and SOLID principles\",\"Participate in code reviews to ensure quality standards and continuous learning\"],\"qualifications_found\":[\"B.Sc. (Hons) in Software Engineering\"],\"recruiter_insights\":[\"Candidate possesses strong foundational skills in web development (HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React) and database management (MySQL), which aligns well with general software developer roles.\",\"Lack of direct experience with .NET, C#, ASP.NET Core, SQL Server, and Oracle is a significant gap given these are mandatory/required for the internship.\",\"Candidate\'s experience with Java, Git, RESTful APIs, and OOP principles are strong assets and directly applicable to parts of the job description.\",\"The candidate demonstrates excellent soft skills including problem-solving, analytical thinking, communication, and teamwork, crucial for an internship environment.\",\"While the candidate has mobile development experience (Flutter), the primary focus of the job description is web applications using .NET technologies.\"],\"requirements_without_evidence\":[\"Basic knowledge of C# and the .NET Framework / .NET Core\",\"Understanding of ASP.NET MVC or ASP.NET Core web application development\",\"Support database operations using Entity Framework Core\"],\"salary_expectation\":\"\"}', NULL, 'Online', '2026-06-27', '09:15', 'http://fcsgdere', '', '2026-06-18 17:14:19', '0', '0', NULL, 'yes');
