obal Resourcing and Talent Management\",\"category\":\"Relevant Skills\",\"experience_level\":\"Advanced\",\"estimated_duration\":\"6–12 Months\",\"evidence_strength\":\"Strong Evidence\",\"evidence_source\":\"Academic Work\",\"usage_context\":\"Studied Global Resourcing and Talent Management as part of Masters.\"},{\"skill\":\"Research Methods\",\"category\":\"Related Skills\",\"experience_level\":\"Advanced\",\"estimated_duration\":\"6–12 Months\",\"evidence_strength\":\"Strong Evidence\",\"evidence_source\":\"Academic Work\",\"usage_context\":\"Studied Research Methods as part of Masters.\"},{\"skill\":\"Employment rights\",\"category\":\"Relevant Skills\",\"experience_level\":\"Advanced\",\"estimated_duration\":\"3+ Years\",\"evidence_strength\":\"Strong Evidence\",\"evidence_source\":\"Professional Experience\",\"usage_context\":\"Acted as a point of contact on all minor queries relating to employment rights.\"},{\"skill\":\"Labour regulations\",\"category\":\"Relevant Skills\",\"experience_level\":\"Advanced\",\"estimated_duration\":\"3+ Years\",\"evidence_strength\":\"Strong Evidence\",\"evidence_source\":\"Professional Experience\",\"usage_context\":\"Acted as a point of contact on all minor queries relating to employment rights.\"}],\"additional_skills\":[\"Microsoft Excel\",\"Leadership\",\"Business Leadership\",\"Marketing\",\"Sales\",\"KPIs\",\"Reporting\"],\"certifications_found\":[\"CIPD qualified\"],\"experience_summary\":\"HR professional with 5 years of experience focusing on recruitment, talent development, and HR operations, including payroll administration and employee engagement. Possesses a strong understanding of employment law and GDPR, with proficiency in HRIS and Microsoft Office applications.\",\"fully_demonstrated_skills\":[\"Payroll administration\",\"Recruitment\",\"Talent development\",\"Employee engagement\",\"Onboarding\",\"Employment law\",\"GDPR\",\"SAP\",\"OpenHire\",\"Microsoft Office\",\"Excel formulas\",\"Access\",\"Performance management\",\"Employee relations\",\"HRIS\",\"Training programs\",\"Succession planning\",\"Employee documentation\",\"Company events\",\"HR operations\",\"Statistical analysis\",\"Customer surveys\",\"Market research\",\"Competitor analysis\",\"Marketing strategy\",\"Business fundamentals\",\"Budget management\",\"Social media advertising\",\"ATS\",\"Job boards\",\"CV screening\",\"Phone interviews\",\"Interview scorecards\",\"Reference checks\",\"Employment contracts\",\"Employee relations matters\",\"Performance improvement plans\",\"Coaching\",\"Mentoring\",\"HR system training\",\"Talent sourcing\",\"Business Studies\",\"Human Resource Management\",\"Leading, Managing and Developing People\",\"Global Resourcing and Talent Management\",\"Research Methods\",\"Employment rights\",\"Labour regulations\"],\"partially_demonstrated_skills\":[\"SAP\",\"OpenHire\",\"Excel formulas\",\"Succession planning\",\"Statistical analysis\",\"Customer surveys\",\"Market research\",\"Competitor analysis\",\"Marketing strategy\",\"Business fundamentals\",\"Budget management\",\"Social media advertising\",\"Business Studies\",\"Leading, Managing and Developing People\",\"Research Methods\"],\"qualifications_found\":[\"Masters Degree\",\"Bachelors Degree\"],\"recruiter_insights\":[\"The candidate has extensive experience in core HR functions including recruitment, talent development, and employee engagement, aligning well with the job description.\",\"Strong experience in implementing and managing HR processes like onboarding, performance reviews, and employee relations.\",\"Candidate has a good understanding of legal aspects such as employment law and GDPR, crucial for HR roles.\",\"Proficiency in relevant HR systems (ATS, SAP, OpenHire) and Microsoft Office Suite, especially Excel and Access.\",\"The candidate\'s Master\'s degree in HR Management and CIPD qualification are highly relevant.\",\"While EPF/ETF claims are not explicitly mentioned, the candidate\'s experience in payroll administration suggests they can adapt.\",\"Demonstrated ability to manage budgets and coordinate events, which are valuable supporting skills.\"],\"requirements_without_evidence\":[\"EPF/ETF claims\"],\"salary_expectation\":\"Not specified\"}', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2026-06-22 12:07:45', '0', '0', NULL, 'pending');
