ant Skills\",\"experience_level\":\"Advanced\",\"estimated_duration\":\"3+ Years\",\"evidence_strength\":\"Strong Evidence\",\"evidence_source\":\"Professional Experience\",\"usage_context\":\"Prepared employment letters and HR correspondence using MS Word.\"},{\"skill\":\"MS PowerPoint\",\"category\":\"Relevant Skills\",\"experience_level\":\"Intermediate\",\"estimated_duration\":\"1–2 Years\",\"evidence_strength\":\"Moderate Evidence\",\"evidence_source\":\"Professional Experience\",\"usage_context\":\"Supported HR reporting and presentations using MS PowerPoint.\"},{\"skill\":\"HR Correspondence\",\"category\":\"Relevant Skills\",\"experience_level\":\"Advanced\",\"estimated_duration\":\"3+ Years\",\"evidence_strength\":\"Strong Evidence\",\"evidence_source\":\"Professional Experience\",\"usage_context\":\"Prepared employment letters, salary confirmations, and HR correspondence.\"}],\"additional_skills\":[\"HRIS & Payroll Systems\",\"Certificate in Payroll Administration\",\"Certificate in Human Resource Management\"],\"certifications_found\":[\"Certificate in Payroll Administration\",\"Certificate in Human Resource Management\"],\"experience_summary\":\"The candidate has over 3 years of experience in HR, with a strong focus on payroll administration, HR operations, and employee lifecycle management. They have demonstrated experience in managing payroll for a significant number of employees, handling attendance, maintaining HRIS, coordinating training, and ensuring compliance. The experience spans two roles, with the most recent being an HR Executive at ABC Manufacturing.\",\"fully_demonstrated_skills\":[\"Attendance Management\",\"Talent Development\",\"Performance Management\",\"MS Excel\",\"HR Operations\"],\"partially_demonstrated_skills\":[\"HRIS and payroll systems\",\"Talent development\",\"Performance management\",\"Employee training\"],\"qualifications_found\":[\"Bachelor of Human Resource Management\"],\"recruiter_insights\":[\"Candidate possesses a strong foundation in core HR functions, particularly payroll and operations, directly aligning with the job requirements.\",\"Experience managing payroll for 300+ employees is a significant asset.\",\"While HRIS and payroll systems are listed, the CV lacks specific details on the systems used, which could be a point of clarification.\",\"The candidate has relevant certifications in Payroll Administration and HRM, complementing their academic qualifications.\",\"The candidate has demonstrated experience in employee engagement and event organization, which is a plus for the role.\"],\"requirements_without_evidence\":[\"Experience working with HRIS and payroll systems (mentioned only as a skill, not detailed usage)\",\"Strong analytical and problem-solving abilities (implied through HR operations, but not explicitly detailed)\",\"Ability to handle confidential information with professionalism and integrity (standard for HR, but not explicitly stated as a demonstrated skill)\",\"Capable of managing multiple priorities and meeting deadlines in a fast-paced environment (implied by experience, but not explicitly stated as a demonstrated skill)\"],\"salary_expectation\":\"Not Specified\"}', NULL, 'On-site', '2026-06-25', '10:00', 'aafwfw', '', '2026-06-22 17:02:36', '0', '0', NULL, 'yes');
