 Filing\",\"Communication\",\"Team Coordination\",\"HTML\",\"CSS\",\"Web Design\"],\"qualifications_found\":[\"Diploma in Accounting and Finance - Colombo Business College, 2023\",\"G.C.E. Advanced Level - Commerce Stream, 2021\"],\"recruiter_insights\":[\"The candidate has foundational experience in core accounting tasks like bookkeeping, invoice processing, and bank reconciliation, aligning well with the Assistant Accountant role.\",\"Strong proficiency in MS Excel is demonstrated, which is a key requirement.\",\"While the candidate has practical experience, the overall experience (0-1 years) and relevant experience (0-1 years) are below the job\'s minimum requirement of 7 years overall and 3 years in a similar role.\",\"The candidate lacks the mandatory qualification of a Bachelor\'s degree in Finance/Accounting from a recognized university or professional qualification (ICASL/CIMA/ACCA).\",\"Skills like HTML, CSS, and JavaScript are present but are additional technical skills and not relevant to this accounting role, though they were used in an academic project.\",\"The candidate demonstrates good soft skills like attention to detail, time management, and record-keeping, which are beneficial.\",\"The duration of experience does not meet the job requirements.\",\"The lack of a Bachelor\'s degree and professional accounting qualification (ICASL/CIMA/ACCA) is a significant gap.\"],\"requirements_without_evidence\":[],\"salary_expectation\":\"Not specified in CV\"}', NULL, 'Online', '2026-06-25', '15:00', 'http://efewfhekjhfwjbfwjhqo', '', '2026-06-23 13:39:26', '1', '0', NULL, 'yes');
