tion\":\"3+ Years\",\"evidence_strength\":\"Strong Evidence\",\"evidence_source\":\"Project\",\"usage_context\":\"Utilized CSS3 for styling the frontend of the Online Bookshop System.\",\"verified\":true}],\"certifications_found\":[\"Python for Beginners in University of Moratuwa\",\"Web Design for Beginners in University of Moratuwa\",\"Introduction to Android Studio Course in Simplilearn\",\"UI/UX for Beginners in Great Learning\",\"ReactJS for Beginners in Simplilearn\"],\"experience_summary\":\"\",\"fully_demonstrated_skills\":[],\"partially_demonstrated_skills\":[\"Bachelor\'s Degree in IT, Computer Science, or related field\"],\"qualifications_found\":[\"B.Sc. (Hons) in Software Engineering\"],\"recruiter_insights\":[\"Overall Match Summary: The candidate\'s profile is strongly oriented towards software development, web/mobile applications, and AI, which presents a significant domain mismatch with the Assistant Manager - IT role that requires expertise in IT infrastructure, SAP, Microsoft 365, IT security, and governance. The candidate also lacks the required minimum 4 years of proven working experience, with their only listed internship scheduled for a future date.\",\"Key Strengths: The candidate demonstrates strong soft skills, including communication, analytical abilities, problem-solving, and teamwork, which are valuable in any professional setting and explicitly sought by the job description.\",\"Related Value: Experience working in an Agile environment during an internship could offer some transferable value in managing IT-related projects, though this is not a core requirement for the role.\",\"Skill Gaps: There are major skill gaps in critical areas such as SAP ERP, Microsoft 365, SharePoint, core networking, CCTV systems, IT security practices (at an organizational level), IT governance, vendor management, data backup/recovery, and general IT infrastructure oversight. The candidate also does not meet the minimum 4 years of proven working experience.\",\"Additional Skills Observation: The candidate possesses an impressive array of technical skills in programming (JavaScript, React, Node.js, Flutter, PHP, MySQL, Python, Java, Dart, Embedded C), AI/ML (LLMs, AI Chatbot Development), and UI/UX design (Figma), which are highly valuable in software engineering but are not relevant to this IT Assistant Manager role.\",\"Risk Notes: The most significant risks are the complete lack of direct relevant experience (0 years to date) compared to the 4-year requirement, and the substantial professional domain mismatch. The candidate\'s expertise is in building software, whereas the job is focused on managing IT systems and infrastructure. The listed internship is in the future, further highlighting the current lack of practical work experience.\",\"Recruiter Recommendation: Not Suitable\"],\"requirements_without_evidence\":[],\"salary_expectation\":\"\"}', NULL, 'On-site', '2026-06-24', '11:00', 'Head office', '', '2026-06-30 10:16:38', '0', '0', NULL, 'yes');
