e. Her background is entirely in finance and accounting, lacking the mandatory IT qualifications and relevant experience specified in the job description.\",\"Key Strengths: The candidate demonstrates strong soft skills such as communication, interpersonal skills, and analytical abilities, which are valuable in any professional setting and were requested in the job description.\",\"Related Value: General professional attributes like time management, confidentiality, and accuracy are present in the candidate\'s profile. While not specific to IT, these support general workplace effectiveness.\",\"Skill Gaps: There is a critical lack of all mandatory and core IT-specific skills and qualifications. These include a Bachelor\'s Degree in IT/Computer Science, minimum 4 years of relevant IT experience, strong knowledge of Microsoft 365, SharePoint, networking, CCTV, IT security, IT governance, SAP, and vendor management.\",\"Additional Skills Observation: The candidate possesses well-demonstrated skills in bookkeeping, invoice processing, financial record keeping, and Microsoft Excel (in a finance context). These skills are robust within the accounting domain but are not relevant to an IT management position.\",\"Risk Notes: The most significant risks are the complete professional domain mismatch and the absence of mandatory qualifications and experience. The listed experience is of short duration and in an unrelated field, posing a high risk for meeting the job\'s technical and leadership requirements.\",\"Recruiter Recommendation: Not Suitable\"],\"requirements_without_evidence\":[],\"salary_expectation\":\"\"}', 'no meet requirements', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2026-06-30 15:10:09', '0', '0', NULL, 'pending');
