sition / Title</td>\r\n      <td style=\'padding:10px 14px;font-size:14px;color:#1e293b;font-weight:600;\'>newwq</td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr><td colspan=\'2\' style=\'height:6px;\'></td></tr>\r\n    \r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td style=\'padding:10px 14px;background:#f8fafc;border-radius:8px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#64748b;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:nowrap;width:35%;\'>Reference No.</td>\r\n      <td style=\'padding:10px 14px;font-size:14px;color:#1e293b;font-weight:600;\'><span style=\'font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;color:#C8A951;\'>GSH/2026/25/004</span></td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr><td colspan=\'2\' style=\'height:6px;\'></td></tr>\r\n    \r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td style=\'padding:10px 14px;background:#f8fafc;border-radius:8px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#64748b;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:nowrap;width:35%;\'>Company</td>\r\n      <td style=\'padding:10px 14px;font-size:14px;color:#1e293b;font-weight:600;\'>George Steuart Health</td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr><td colspan=\'2\' style=\'height:6px;\'></td></tr>\r\n    \r\n            </table>\r\n          </div>\r\n\r\n          <!-- Note -->\r\n          <div style=\'background:#fff7ed;border:1px solid #fed7aa;border-radius:10px;padding:14px 18px;margin-bottom:28px;\'>\r\n            <p style=\'margin:0 0 4px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#c2410c;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;\'>&#9888;&nbsp; Action Required</p>\r\n            <p style=\'margin:0 0 8px;font-size:13px;color:#475569;\'>Please log in to the Careers Portal and review this requisition. You can approve it to make it live, or reject it with a reason.</p>\r\n          </div>\r\n\r\n          <!-- CTA Button -->\r\n          <div style=\'text-align:center;margin-bottom:8px;\'>\r\n            \r\n    <table cellpadding=\'0\' cellspacing=\'0\' style=\'margin:0 auto;\'>\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <td align=\'center\' style=\'border-radius:10px;background:#2a