y:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;margin-right:6px;margin-top:-2px;\'></span>\r\n      <span style=\'vertical-align:middle;\'>Awaiting Global Approval</span>\r\n    </span>\r\n    </div>\r\n          <h2 style=\'margin:0 0 12px;font-size:20px;font-weight:800;color:#1a0208;line-height:1.3;\'>Resubmitted Requisition Created by Sub Admin 1 — Your Action Required</h2>\r\n\r\n          <!-- Intro -->\r\n          <p style=\'margin:0 0 24px;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.6;\'>A job vacancy requisition has been <strong>revised and resubmitted directly by Sub Admin 1</strong>, and is now awaiting your final approval as <strong>Global Admin</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n          <!-- Vacancy Info Card -->\r\n          <div style=\'background:#f8fafc;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;border-radius:12px;padding:20px;margin-bottom:24px;\'>\r\n            <p style=\'margin:0 0 14px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#94a3b8;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;\'>Requisition Details</p>\r\n            <table width=\'100%\' cellpadding=\'0\' cellspacing=\'0\'>\r\n              \r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td style=\'padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9;\'>\r\n        <div style=\'font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:#64748b;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1.2px;margin-bottom:4px;\'>Position / Title</div>\r\n        <div style=\'font-size:14px;color:#1e293b;font-weight:600;line-height:1.4;\'>111q</div>\r\n      </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    \r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td style=\'padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9;\'>\r\n        <div style=\'font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:#64748b;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1.2px;margin-bottom:4px;\'>Reference No.</div>\r\n        <div style=\'font-size:14px;color:#1e293b;font-weight:600;line-height:1.4;\'><span style=\'font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;color:#C8A951;\'>GSH/2026/25/005</span></div>\r\n      </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    \r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td style=\'padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #