background:#f8fafc;border-top:1px solid #e2e8f0;border-radius:0 0 15px 15px;padding:20px 36px;text-align:center;\'>\r\n                <p style=\'margin:0;font-size:11px;color:#94a3b8;line-height:1.6;\'>\r\n                  This is an automated notification from the George Steuart Careers Portal.<br>\r\n                  Please do not reply directly to this email.\r\n                </p>\r\n                <p style=\'margin:8px 0 0;font-size:10px;color:#cbd5e1;\'>\r\n                  &copy; 2026 George Steuart &amp; Company Ltd. All rights reserved.\r\n                </p>\r\n              </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n\r\n          </table>\r\n        </td></tr>\r\n      </table>\r\n    </body>\r\n    </html>\r\n    ', 'sent', '1', NULL, '2026-06-25 09:07:48', '2026-06-25 09:20:08');
